Name: AllLanguages
Title: All Languages
Descriptino: This value set includes all possible codes from BCP-47 (see http://tools.ietf.org/html/bcp47)

Name: CombinedDoseForm
Title: Combined Dose Form
Descriptino: Dose forms for a product as a whole, considering all individual parts, but before any mixing

Name: CountryValueSet
Title: Country ValueSet
Descriptino: This value set defines a base set of codes for countries.             Note: The codes for countries are taken from    [ISO 3166](https://www.iso.org/iso-3166-country-codes.html).

Name: IdentifierTypeCodes
Title: Identifier Type Codes
Descriptino: A coded type for an identifier that can be used to determine which identifier to use for a specific purpose.

Name: IdentifierUse
Title: IdentifierUse
Descriptino: Identifies the purpose for this identifier, if known .

Name: IngredientFunction
Title: Ingredient Function
Descriptino: A classification of the ingredient identifying its precise purpose(s) in the drug product (beyond e.g. active/inactive).

Name: IngredientManufacturerRole
Title: Ingredient Manufacturer Role
Descriptino: The way in which this manufacturer is associated with the ingredient. For example whether it is a possible one (others allowed), or an exclusive authorized one for this ingredient. Note that this is not the manufacturing process role.

Name: IngredientRole
Title: Ingredient Role
Descriptino: A classification of the ingredient identifying its purpose within the product.

Name: JurisdictionValueSet
Title: Jurisdiction ValueSet
Descriptino: This value set defines a base set of codes for country, country subdivision and region    for indicating where a resource is intended to be used.             Note: The codes for countries and country subdivisions are taken from    [ISO 3166](https://www.iso.org/iso-3166-country-codes.html)    while the codes for "supra-national" regions are from    [UN Standard country or area codes for statistical use (M49)](http://unstats.un.org/unsd/methods/m49/m49.htm).

Name: CommonLanguages
Title: Common Languages
Descriptino: This value set includes common codes from BCP-47 (see http://tools.ietf.org/html/bcp47)

Name: LegalStatusOfSupply
Title: Legal Status Of Supply
Descriptino: The prescription supply types appropriate to a medicinal product

Name: SNOMEDCTMedicationCodes
Title: SNOMED CT Medication Codes
Descriptino: This value set includes all drug or medicament substance codes and all pharmaceutical/biologic products from SNOMED CT - provided as an exemplar value set.

Name: AdditionalMonitoring
Title: Additional Monitoring
Descriptino: Extra monitoring defined for a Medicinal Product.

Name: ProductClassification
Title: Product Classification
Descriptino: This value set includes codes from the Anatomical Therapeutic Chemical Classification System - provided as an exemplar value set.

Name: ProductConfidentiality
Title: Product Confidentiality
Descriptino: Confidentiality rating, e.g. commercial sensitivity for a Medicinal Product.

Name: ProductContactType
Title: Product Contact Type
Descriptino: Contact type for a Medicinal Product.

Name: ProductCrossReferenceType
Title: Product Cross Reference Type
Descriptino: Relationship to another Medicinal Product.

Name: MedicinalProductDomain
Title: Medicinal Product Domain
Descriptino: Applicable domain for this product (e.g. human, veterinary)

Name: ProductNamePartType
Title: Product Name Part Type
Descriptino: Type of part of a name for a Medicinal Product.

Name: ProductNameType
Title: Product Name Type
Descriptino: Type of a name for a Medicinal Product.

Name: MedicinalProductPackageType
Title: Medicinal Product Package Type
Descriptino: Types of medicinal product packs

Name: PediatricUse
Title: Pediatric Use
Descriptino: Extra measures defined for a Medicinal Product, such as heightened reporting requirements.

Name: SpecialMeasures
Title: Special Measures
Descriptino: Extra measures defined for a Medicinal Product, such as a requirement to conduct post-authorization studies.

Name: MedicinalProductType
Title: Medicinal Product Type
Descriptino: Overall defining type of this Medicinal Product.

Name: PackageMaterial
Title: Package Material
Descriptino: A material used in the construction of packages and their components.

Name: PackageType
Title: Package Type
Descriptino: A high level categorisation of a package.

Name: PackagingType
Title: Packaging Type
Descriptino: A type of packaging.

Name: ProductCharacteristic
Title: Product Characteristic
Descriptino: This value set includes all observable entity codes from SNOMED CT - provided as an exemplar value set.

Name: ProductIntendedUse
Title: Product Intended Use
Descriptino: The overall intended use of a product.

Name: PublicationStatus
Title: PublicationStatus
Descriptino: The lifecycle status of an artifact.

Name: QuantityComparator
Title: QuantityComparator
Descriptino: How the Quantity should be understood and represented.

Name: RegulatedAuthorizationBasis
Title: Regulated Authorization Basis
Descriptino: A legal or regulatory framework against which an authorization is granted, or other reasons for it.

Name: RegulatedAuthorizationCaseType
Title: Regulated Authorization Case Type
Descriptino: The type of a case involved in an application.

Name: RegulatedAuthorizationType
Title: Regulated Authorization Type
Descriptino: Overall type of this authorization.

Name: ResourceType
Title: Resource Types
Descriptino: Concrete FHIR Resource Types

Name: SNOMEDCTRouteCodes
Title: SNOMED CT Route Codes
Descriptino: This value set includes all Route codes from SNOMED CT - provided as an exemplar.

Name: SNOMEDCTSubstanceCodes
Title: SNOMED CT Substance Codes
Descriptino: This value set includes all substance codes from SNOMED CT - provided as an exemplar value set.

Name: LegalStatusForTheSupplyVs
Title: The Legal Status of Supply Value Set

Name: PharmaceuticalDoseFormVs
Title: The Pharmaceutical Dose Form Value Set

Name: MedicinalProductNamePartTypeVs
Title: The Medicinal Product Name Part Type

Name: RegulatoryEntitlementStatusVs
Title: The Regulatory Entitlement Status Value Set

Name: RegulatoryEntitlementTypeVs
Title: The Regulatory Entitlement Type Value Set

Title: The Units of Presentation Value Set
